# Vert.x starters

## Description

Maven Vert.x starter parent project, with modules showing basic development cases.

## Requirements

* Java 11
* Maven 3.8 

## Current stack

* Vert.x 4.3
* JUnit 5

## References

https://sdkman.io/
https://vertx.io/docs/vertx-core/java/
https://github.com/vert-x3/vertx-maven-starter
http://tutorials.jenkov.com/vert.x/verticles.html

## Notes

### Build and run all modules

$ ./smoke-test.sh -v -f 0 -t 20

### New module workflow

#### Macos, part 1.

$ git status
$ mvn clean
$ git branch -a
$ git checkout -b 21
$ cp -pvri 20 21
$ sed -i "" -e "s/^  <\/modules>/    <module>21<\/module>\n  <\/modules>/" pom.xml
$ less pom.xml 
$ sed -i "" -e "s/vertx-starter-[0-9]\{2\}/vertx-starter-21/" 21/pom.xml
$ less 21/pom.xml 
$ sed -i "" -e "s/Module 20/Module 21/" 21/README
$ sed -i "" -e "s/vertx-starter-[0-9]\{2\}/vertx-starter-21/" 21/README
$ less 21/README 
$ cd 21

#### Linux, part 1.

$ git status
$ mvn clean
$ git branch -a
$ git checkout -b 21
$ cp -pvri 20 21
$ sed -i -e 's/^  <\/modules>/    <module>21<\/module>\n  <\/modules>/' pom.xml
$ less pom.xml 
$ sed -i -e 's/vertx-starter-[0-9]\{2\}/vertx-starter-21/' 21/pom.xml
$ less 21/pom.xml 
$ sed -i -e 's/Module 20/Module 21/' 21/README
$ sed -i -e 's/vertx-starter-[0-9]\{2\}/vertx-starter-21/' 21/README
$ less 21/README 
$ cd 21

#### All, part 2.

(work)*

$ ./redeploy.sh 
$ mvn clean package
$ java -jar target/*fat.jar 
$ cd ..
$ git status
$ git add pom.xml 21
$ git commit -m "Add module 21"
$ mvn clean
$ git checkout master
$ git merge 21
$ git log
$ git tag -a 21-module-workflow -m "Module workflow example"
$ git push origin master --tags
$ git branch -d 21

